Creates a new ExpandedRouteLandmarkItem.

Parameters:
type The type of landmark, BUA, railway etc.
location How the landmark is located relative the route.
side Which side of the road the landmark is if appropriate.
atTurn If the landmark is at the turn or if it is passed on the way to the turn.
importance How important the landmark is, undefined.
dist How far on the route-item is the landmark located.
name The name(s) of the landmark, the ownership is transfered to this class.
